- made the generated thumbnails larger and the text more compact across
  the whole generated site. Note that this requires removing your entire
  thumbnails/ directory in the generated HTML directory so that they can
  be regenerated.
- search page now acts as a single page application and is much faster
- photo/video metadata on the search page now matches what's on the
  staticly-generated pages
- add optional support for converting videos to a common format via the
  new command line arguments --video-convert-command and
  --video-convert-ext
- add search links to the statically-generated event and tag pages
- fix for searching for text fields that have multiple values
- hide the keyboard on mobile on the search page after enter has been pressed
- add 'CSV Download' link to the search page
